1 in 1999 and 2000, the plaintiff (meadow springs) undertook a project to build and then sell 54 serviced apartments adjacent to a golf course at meadow springs, a location near mandurah in western australia.
in order to finance the project, meadow springs raised $4.85 million in capital by the issue of shares, and borrowed in the vicinity of $7.47 million.
